                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <span>📍</span>
                        <span>Dwarka, Delhi</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <span>⏱️</span>
                        <span>2 weeks</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
